  "text": "Since it is more complex to analyze directly piezoelectric frame structure modal, in order to more clearly describe the optimization methods in the paper, the constituent units of the piezoelectric frame structure (i.e., piezoelectric beam) are directly analyzed. The material of the framework is aluminum alloy, and its related parameters are as follows: length = 1500 mm, width = 20mm, height ℎ = 5mm, density = 2700 kg/m 3 , Young's modulus = 7.0 × 10 10 Pa, and Poisson's ratio ] = 0.33. Material type of piezoelectric sensors is P-51, material type of piezoelectric actuator is PZT-5H, and its parameters are shown in Table 1 [CITATION_1] .",
